    "description": "AIIMS, one of India's leading organizations, is hiring a Surgeon for our Rajkot operations. We offer a competitive salary package along with world-class benefits.\n\nAbout AIIMS:\nAIIMS is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Provide high-quality patient care and maintain patient records\n• Administer medications and treatments as prescribed\n• Collaborate with pharmaceutical representatives and medical suppliers\n• Maintain sterile environments and follow infection control protocols\n• Diagnose and treat medical conditions following established protocols\n• Educate patients and families on health management and disease prevention\n• Coordinate with multidisciplinary teams for comprehensive patient management\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBBS / MD / MS from recognized medical college\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Patient Care\n• Proficiency in Medical Coding\n• Proficiency in ICD-10\n• Proficiency in EMR/EHR\n• Proficiency in Surgical Procedures\n• Proficiency in Diagnostic Skills\n• Proficiency in Medical Terminology\n• Proficiency in Clinical Documentation\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Referral bonus program\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Rajkot, Gujarat, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with AIIMS!",
